<P>
4 DIE AS PLANE HITS DITCH 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By Associated Press 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>
<P>
OTTAWA, Ohio 
</P>
</DATELINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Four people aboard a single-engine airplane were killed when the plane came 
down on U.S. 224 near here, skidded into a ditch and burst into flames, 
officials said. The cause of the crash Sunday night was not determined 
immediately. 
</P>
