<TEXT>
<P>
Rose L. Rashmir, 90, former board chairman for the Suicide Prevention Center at 
UCLA. Mrs. Rashmir was a researcher and social worker in her native New York 
and treasurer of an electrical contracting firm in New Haven, Conn. 
</P>
