<LENGTH>
<P>
67 words 
</P>
</LENGTH>
<HEADLINE>
<P>
PEOPLE 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Sega of America, South San Francisco, named Thomas Kalinske president. Kalinske 
was most recently president and chief executive officer of Matchbox 
International Ltd. and president of Universal Matchbox Group. Before that he 
was president of Mattel Inc. Sega sells electronic entertainment products, 
including coin-operated video arcade machines, home video game hardware and 
software and toys. 
</P>
