might arise as Everest &amp; Jennings seeks to reach agreement with its primary 
domestic lender on long-term financing arrangements. The wheelchair 
manufacturer has been operating for several weeks on the basis of informal 
day-to-day waivers and extensions by its primary domestic lender. 
