across the Southland, helping spread fires that scorched more than two dozen 
homes. Blazes erupted in L.A., Riverside and San Bernardino counties. 
Firefighter checked charred roof of home in Diamond Bar, above. ; Photo, Dennis 
West consoles wife Carol after a brush fire, possibly started by illegal 
fireworks, destroyed most of their house in Diamond Bar. ; Photo, A 
