<P>
REGIONAL EARNINGS: CALIFORNIA AMPLIFIER'S QUARTERLY INCOME UP 40% 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
California Amplifier, a Camarillo company that makes components for satellite 
dishes and other devices, said its net income for the second quarter that ended 
Sept. 1 soared 40% to $111,000 from $79,000 a year ago. 
</P>
<P>
