APSB BANCORP'S PROFIT INCREASES 30% FOR QUARTER 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
APSB Bancorp, the Sherman Oaks-based parent of American Pacific State Bank, 
said its third-quarter profit rose 30% from a year earlier, to $566,000 from 
