$177 million a year earlier. The asset growth was aided by APSB's opening of a 
new office in Woodland Hills. 
</P>
<P>
APSB, which has five branch offices, attributed the profit gain to cost 
controls and strong loan demand, particularly for its Small Business 
Administration loans. 
