most combustive live performers. ; Photo, Queen Latifah brought to the stage 
exuberant personality. ; Photo, Rocker Ian Astbury, who came up with the idea 
of the festival. ; Photo, Indigo Girls Amy Ray, left, and Emily Sailers perform 
at "A Gathering of the Tribes" festival in Costa Mesa. JOHN FUNG / Los Angeles 
