</P>
<P>
Measuring consumer confidence 
</P>
<P>
A survey of 1,016 Orange County consumers shows that they think tough economic 
times have arrived and that this is not a good period to make big-ticket 
purchases. Still, most local consumers feel that they are better off 
financially than a year ago. 
</P>
<P>
* Is the United States in for good or bad times next year? 
</P>
